oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Quartermaster return for Henry County Confederates
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: List of clothing and personal supplies such as knives, hats, blankets, shirts & coats issued to named members of various Henry County-based Confederate units, i.e. the 5th Tenn. Inf., the 46th Tenn. Inf., and the 154 (Senior) Tenn. Inf. CSA.
